142
00:10:36,470 --> 00:10:36,820
Yes.

143
00:11:00,960 --> 00:11:01,640
Mr. Jiang.

144
00:11:02,140 --> 00:11:03,310
Are you okay?

145
00:11:04,030 --> 00:11:04,600
How about

146
00:11:04,770 --> 00:11:06,250
I buy you a

147
00:11:06,520 --> 00:11:08,050
