188
00:13:07,590 --> 00:13:08,850
My mother didn't hit me

189
00:13:09,630 --> 00:13:10,740
to teach me.

190
00:13:11,660 --> 00:13:12,430
She just

191
00:13:12,620 --> 00:13:13,700
felt like

192
00:13:14,270 --> 00:13:15,330
