224
00:14:21,180 --> 00:14:22,970
I'm not someone's punching bag either.

225
00:14:22,970 --> 00:14:23,430
I...

226
00:14:29,470 --> 00:14:30,550
So do you know

227
00:14:31,580 --> 00:14:32,910
why I always

228
00:14:32,950 --> 00:14:34,140
I ask you to stop

229
00:14:34,160 --> 00:14:35,690
