265
00:16:27,670 --> 00:16:28,390
Of course.

266
00:16:28,870 --> 00:16:30,890
Whether it's then or now,

267
00:16:31,050 --> 00:16:32,550
I'll stand behind you.

268
00:16:39,070 --> 00:16:39,630
Tong Wan.

269
00:16:39,910 --> 00:16:40,590
Can I

