284
00:17:09,260 --> 00:17:09,790
Tong Wan.

285
00:17:10,920 --> 00:17:11,720
I think

286
00:17:13,250 --> 00:17:15,109
you are especially suited to be my

287
00:17:16,700 --> 00:17:17,470
mother.

288
00:17:22,030 --> 00:17:23,890
